International Components for Unicode (ICU) root resource bundle source file.
This file defines all resources used by the Facsimile library.

This file is populated using the US-English (en_US) locale, which will become
the default for missing locales.  (That is, say a user prefers a Mexican
Spanish locale, but none is available - and no generic Spanish locale is
available either, then they will get US-English).

Bear in mind that when changing resource definitions here, corresponding
modifications may also need to be made to other English locales.
